---
title: Caribbean Spiced BBQ Pork Fried Rice with Sweetcorn and Spinach
description: This Caribbean Spiced BBQ Pork Fried Rice is a crowd pleaser and is one to get the family round the dinner table for. Super simple to make, and easily customised to suit the kids too.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y23_R11_W29_UK_F13720-6_Main_low-dbabb3ad.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipecards/card/646645c76ced9aa0d6353cd5.pdf
time required: 20 minutes
source: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipes/caribbean-spiced-bbq-pork-fried-rice-646645c76ced9aa0d6353cd5
author: Sam Richards
servings: 2
cuisine: Caribbean
